   <p>2 Beds | 1 Bath</p>\n                        <p>A bright and airy space in the heart of downtown.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$350,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/3498db/ffffff?text=Family+House\" alt=\"Family House\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h4>Cozy Suburban Family Home</h4>\n                        <p>4 Beds | 2.5 Baths</p>\n                        <p>Perfect for families, with a spacious backyard.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$520,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"property-card\">\n                    <img src=\"https://via.placeholder.com/300x200/3498db/ffffff?text=Seaside+Cottage\" alt=\"Seaside Cottage\">\n                    <div class=\"property-info\">\n                        <h4>Tranquil Seaside Cottage</h4>\n                        <p>3 Beds | 2 Baths</p>\n                        <p>Enjoy peaceful ocean views from your own getaway.</p>\n                        <p class=\"price\">$480,000</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <section id=\"contact\">\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <h3>Get In Touch</h3>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.2em; margin-bottom: 30px;\">\n                Ready to find your cozy corner? We're here to help.\n            </p>\n            <p style=\"font-size: 1.1em;\">\n                Email: info@cozyhomesrealty.com<br>\n                Phone: (123) 456-7890<br>\n                Address: 123 Cozy Lane, Homewood, CA 90210\n            </p>\n        </div>\n    </section>\n    <footer>\n        <div class=\"container\">\n            <p>&copy; 2023 Cozy Homes Realty. All rights reserved.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n</body>\n</html>"}